/# Este fluxo funciona para descompactar arquivos no aplicativo winrar. Caso você tenha o aplicativo 7z, esse fluxo não vai funcionar. 
#/
Folder.GetFiles Folder: caminho_pasta FileFilter: $'''*.rar''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos
/# Ele obtem todos os arquivos da pasta e das subpastas dentro dela
#/
LOOP FOREACH item_rar IN arquivos
    System.RunApplication.RunApplication ApplicationPath: item_rar WindowStyle: System.ProcessWindowStyle.Maximized
    WAIT 4
    IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['Imagem 1']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
        MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['Imagem 1']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.Instant Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy X=> X Y=> Y
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        GOTO Continuar
    END
    IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnForeground Images: [imgrepo['Imagem 2']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
        MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['Imagem 2']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.Instant Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy X=> X Y=> Y
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    END
    LABEL Continuar
    MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['Extrair']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.Instant Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy X=> X2 Y=> Y2
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Extraction path and options''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%caminho_pasta%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT 2
    IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Confirm file replace''' Class: $'''''') THEN
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Tab}{Tab}{Tab}{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    END
    WAIT 2
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
END
